  "title": "-NEW- 12 Months Risk Program Operations Analyst (Financial Services)",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>·       \nSupport\nthe design, implementation, and ongoing enhancement of a regional merchant risk\nprogram, including frameworks, workflows, and governance.</p><p>·       \nMonitor,\ninvestigate, and report on program performance using data analytics,\ndashboards, and operational metrics.</p><p>·       \nManage\nnotifications, follow-ups, and billing of program fees and non-compliance\nassessments where applicable.</p><p>·       \nCommunicate\nprogram identifications, status updates, and remediation requirements to\ninternal stakeholders and external clients.</p><p>·       \nCollaborate\nwith regional markets and support centres to ensure consistent understanding\nand execution of program requirements.</p><p>·       \nContribute\nto automation initiatives and tool design to improve efficiency, scalability,\nand data quality.</p><p>·       \nDocument\nprocesses, controls, and operational procedures to support audit and compliance\nneeds.</p><p>·       \nAdhoc\ntasks and projects as assigned<br />\n<br />\n</p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>·       \nMinimum\nDegree in a related discipline</p><p>·       \nRisk experience within the fintech/payments\nindustry would be an added advantage </p><p>·       \nAble to\nstart immediately or within short notice</p><p><br />\n<br />\n</p><p>Interested candidates, kindly\nemail your detailed resumes in MS word format to <a href=\"mailto:josephkoh@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joseph.koh@ambition.com.sg</a>\n</p><p>Attention to Joseph Koh Wei Jie\n(R1873431)</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be\nnotified</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Registration Number: R1873431</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment\npurposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number:\n200611680D. License Number: 10C5117</p>",
